critter.name: Wharf Roach
critter.desc: The wharf roach is an omnivore, which is merely a polite way of saying it will eat almost anything. This skittering scavenger and its uncouth appetite help keep beaches clean, it's said. But I dare say, their long antenna and bulging eyes turn MY stomach. Unappetizing indeed...
critter.quote: I caught a wharf roach! This water-loving roach has no pier!
